## About FightTheStroke Foundation

FightTheStroke Foundation was founded by Francesca Fedeli and Roberto
D'Angelo after their son Mario experienced a stroke at birth. The
foundation supports children with cerebral palsy and their families
through innovative rehabilitation, advocacy, and inclusion programs.

Learn more: fightthestroke.org

